<br>
She finally got through the gates at the bottom, having a few conflicts with the guards. She decided to transport herself to the top directly. <br>
<br>
In a mist of golden light and silver dust she appeared standing at the entrance of the Main Throne Room. She stood there with her head slightly bowed to the Gods in respect. She could care less about worshipping them, for her own ways as well as Eli's were in her head. However, she had great respect for them. Especially Hera, The Furies, Artemis, Athena and Dite. Figurably, the Goddesses instead of the men.<br>
<br>
