<br>
&quot;I come bringing news to share with my Goddesses. And in asking of a blessing. Eli, the Devi from India has asked my hand in marriage. I have consented to it.&quot; She smiled.<br>
<br>
&quot;I and you all know that because Scynthia lies on Ancient Amazon Grounds, I do not need the blessings of Olympian Gods because of the ways that we follow. I myself am a Goddess of such order by your rites, and in equality of eachother, I ask a blessing from you on my marriage to the Avatar.&quot;<br>
<br>
She smiled to Hera. Then her eyes moved to Aphrodite.<br>
<br>
&quot;Especially from you Love Goddess. It is good to see you Aphrodite.&quot;<br>
<br>
Her eyes turned to Athena and Artemis in great respect.<br>
<br>
&quot;Because of my ties to the amazons, I ask for your blessings as well dear Goddess Sisters.&quot;<br>
<br>
She stood there awaiting the replies from the Gods. . . <br>
