<br>
&quot;Unbeliever you say? Well who said that I was an Elisian? I only am marrying one Zeus.&quot;<br>
<br>
She then took a few steps around the area in which the other Gods stood.<br>
<br>
&quot;And I am welcome here as much as any of the other Gods and Goddesses. For I hold the title of such.&quot;<br>
<br>
