<br>
Alecto looked at Zeus while Megaera and Tisiphone went to see Alysia.<br>
<br>
Alecto looked serious for once in her life.<br>
&quot;I ask that you respect this dear Amazon Nephew, for it was she who saved our world from that of the Alternate one. The Alternate Universe in which our own Queen was harmed. Alysia's son there, sacrificed his own blood to seal the portal.&quot;<br>
<br>
She looked back at Megaera as Meg stepped forward.<br>
